25#include <sys/cdefs.h>
26__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_bios_shadowpci.c,v 1.3 2018/08/27 07:42:02 riastradh Exp $");
27
28#include "priv.h"
29
30#include <core/pci.h>
31
32#ifdef __NetBSD__
33# define __iomem __pci_rom_iomem
34#endif
35
36struct priv {
37 struct pci_dev *pdev;
38 void __iomem *rom;
39 size_t size;
40};
41
42static u32
43pcirom_read(void *data, u32 offset, u32 length, struct nvkm_bios *bios)
44{
45 struct priv *priv = data;
46 if (offset + length <= priv->size) {
47 memcpy_fromio(bios->data + offset,
48 (const char __iomem *)priv->rom + offset, length);
49 return length;
50 }
51 return 0;
52}
53
54static void
55pcirom_fini(void *data)
56{
57 struct priv *priv = data;
58 pci_unmap_rom(priv->pdev, priv->rom);
59 pci_disable_rom(priv->pdev);
60 kfree(priv);
61}
62
63static void *
64pcirom_init(struct nvkm_bios *bios, const char *name)
65{
66 struct nvkm_device *device = bios->subdev.device;
67 struct priv *priv = NULL;
68 struct pci_dev *pdev;
69 int ret;
70
71 if (device->func->pci)
72 pdev = device->func->pci(device)->pdev;
73 else
74 return ERR_PTR(-ENODEV);
75
76 if (!(ret = pci_enable_rom(pdev))) {
77 if (ret = -ENOMEM,
78 (priv = kmalloc(sizeof(*priv), GFP_KERNEL))) {
79 if (ret = -EFAULT,
80 (priv->rom = pci_map_rom(pdev, &priv->size))) {
81 priv->pdev = pdev;
82 return priv;
83 }
84 kfree(priv);
85 }
86 pci_disable_rom(pdev);
87 }
88
89 return ERR_PTR(ret);
90}
91
92const struct nvbios_source
93nvbios_pcirom = {
94 .name = "PCIROM",
95 .init = pcirom_init,
96 .fini = pcirom_fini,
97 .read = pcirom_read,
98 .rw = true,
99};
100
101static void *
102platform_init(struct nvkm_bios *bios, const char *name)
103{
104 struct nvkm_device *device = bios->subdev.device;
105 struct pci_dev *pdev;
106 struct priv *priv;
107 int ret = -ENOMEM;
108
109 if (device->func->pci)
110 pdev = device->func->pci(device)->pdev;
111 else
112 return ERR_PTR(-ENODEV);
113
114 if ((priv = kmalloc(sizeof(*priv), GFP_KERNEL))) {
115 if (ret = -ENODEV,
116 (priv->rom = pci_platform_rom(pdev, &priv->size)))
117 return priv;
118 kfree(priv);
119 }
120
121 return ERR_PTR(ret);
122}
123
124const struct nvbios_source
125nvbios_platform = {
126 .name = "PLATFORM",
127 .init = platform_init,
128 .fini = (void(*)(void *))kfree,
129 .read = pcirom_read,
130 .rw = true,
131};
